contentrichtext.text: '''Radio Luxembourg''' may refer to: * [[Radio Luxembourg (English)]], a commercial radio station in English, begun in 1933 and closed in 1992 * Radio Luxembourg, now known as [[RTL (French radio)|RTL]], a French-language commercial radio station begun in 1933 * Radio Luxemburg, now [[RTL Radio]], a German-language station begun after World War II * [[Radio 1212]], an Allied black propaganda radio station operated from 1944 to 1945 * [[Radio Luxembourg (DRM)]], a commercial station begun in 2005 __NOTOC__ {{disambig}}
